Daniel Benson (born in 1997) better known by his stage name Buju or Bujutoyourears is an Nigerian Afro fusion singer, songwriter and record producer.
Born in Lagos Buju was previously signed to Burna Boy's Spaceship Records.
In 2019, he was nominated for the "Rookie of the Year" category at The Headies 2019.
